README.md

Awesome

   [https://travis-ci.org/pehapkari/awesome-symfony-education]Build Status

   A curated list of amazingly awesome Symfony articles, series and books.

   For bundles selection, check
   [https://github.com/sitepoint-editors/awesome-symfony]sitepoint-editors
   /awesome-symfony.

Single Action Controller

     * [https://dunglas.fr/2016/01/dunglasactionbundle-symfony-controllers
       -redesigned/]DunglasActionBundle: Symfony controllers, redesigned
       [2016]
     * [https://beberlei.de/2014/04/24/symfony_hello_world.html]Symfony
       Hello World [2014]

Tutorials and Video Courses

     * [https://knpuniversity.com/tracks/symfony]KnpUniversity - Symfony
       Course Track
          + Videos + articles. Straightforward, simple & with examples.
     * [https://code.tutsplus.com/series/working-with-symfony-2--cms-636]W
       orking with Symfony 2
          + Short video series for starters
     * [https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL3Wxyd2R8-gIuToQ1NmhVSLZfjr
       BMePNu]Symfony 2 - under 5 minutes
          + Short video series for starters

Series for begginers

     * [https://knpuniversity.com/screencast/symfony]Joyful Development
       with Symfony 3 [2016] by KnpUniversity
     * [https://www.zdrojak.cz/serialy/symfony-po-kruckach/]Symfony po
       kruckách na Zdroják.cz [2015/2016] [cesky]

Dependency Injection

     * [https://www.tomasvotruba.cz/blog/2017/05/07/how-to-refactor-to-new
       -dependency-injection-features-in-symfony-3-3/]How to refactor to
       new Dependency Injection features in Symfony 3.3 by Tomas Votruba
       [2017]

EventDispatcher

     * [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K9jub4JPpcc]Decouple your
       application with (Domain-)Events by Benjamin Eberlei [2013]
     * [http://mmoreram.com/blog/2015/08/20/re-thinking-event-listeners/]R
       e-thinking Event Listeners [2015]
     * [https://knpuniversity.com/screencast/symfony-journey]Journey to
       the Center of Symfony: HttpKernel Request-Response by KnpUniversity
       [2015]

Security

     * [https://stovepipe.systems/post/symfony-security-roles-vs-voters]Sy
       mfony Security, Roles vs. Voters [2015]
     * [https://jolicode.com/blog/do-not-use-fosuserbundle]Do not use
       FOSUserBundle [2015]
     * [https://knpuniversity.com/screencast/new-in-symfony3/voter]The new
       Voter Class [2016] by KnpUniversity

Forms

     * [https://blog.martinhujer.cz/symfony-forms-with-request-objects/]Do
       n't Use Entities in Symfony Forms. Use Custom Data Objects Instead
       [2017]
     * [https://stovepipe.systems/post/avoiding-entities-in-forms]Avoiding
       Entities in Forms [2016]
     * [https://stovepipe.systems/post/rethinking-form-development]Rethink
       ing Form Development [2016]

Doctrine

     * [https://www.tomasvotruba.cz/blog/2017/10/16/how-to-use-repository-
       with-doctrine-as-service-in-symfony/]How to use Repository with
       Doctrine as Service in Symfony [2017]
     * [http://labs.octivi.com/mastering-symfony2-performance-doctrine/]Ma
       stering Symfony2 Performance - Doctrine [2014]
     * [https://www.slideshare.net/_leopro_/rich-domain-model-with-symfony
       -25-and-doctrine-25]Rich domain model with Symfony 2.5 and Doctrine
       2.5 [2014]

Translations

     * [https://developer.happyr.com/how-happyr-work-with-symfony-translat
       ions]How Happyr work with Symfony translations [2015]
     * [https://jolicode.com/blog/translation-workflow-with-symfony2]Trans
       lation workflow with Symfony2 [2015]
     * [http://obtao.com/blog/2013/06/how-to-organize-your-translations-in
       -symfony/]How to organize your translations in Symfony [2013]

Bundles

     * [https://www.slideshare.net/matthiasnoback/high-quality-symfony-bun
       dles-tutorial-dutch-php-conference-2014]High Quality Symfony
       Bundles [2014]

Decoupling

     * [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0L_9NutiJlc]The Framework as an
       implementation by Marcello Duarte & Konstantin Kudryashov [2013],
       [https://github.com/MarcelloDuarte/hexagonal-symfony]Github
       repository
     * [https://matthiasnoback.nl/2014/06/how-to-create-framework-independ
       ent-controllers/]Symfony2: How to create framework independent
       controllers [2014]

Legacy

     * [https://speakerdeck.com/hhamon/bringing-symfony-components-into-yo
       ur-legacy-code]Bringing Symfony Components into Your Legacy Code
       [2016]
     * [https://speakerdeck.com/jakzal/eating-spaghetti-with-symfony]Eatin
       g spaghetti with Symfony [2016]
     * [https://stovepipe.systems/post/migrating-your-project-to-symfony]M
       igrating your project to Symfony [2016]

Performance

     * [http://labs.octivi.com/mastering-symfony2-performance-internals/]M
       astering Symfony2 Performance - Internals [2014]
     * [https://tideways.io/profiler/blog/5-ways-to-optimize-symfony-basel
       ine-performance]5 Ways to optimize Symfony Baseline Performance
       [2015]

DDD

     * [http://williamdurand.fr/2013/08/07/ddd-with-symfony2-folder-struct
       ure-and-code-first/]DDD with Symfony2: Folder Structure And Code
       First [2013]

General

     * [http://www.thisprogrammingthing.com/2016/lessons-from-my-first-sym
       fony-project/]Lessons Learned from My First Symfony Project [2016]
     * [http://blog.kevingomez.fr/2014/04/08/symfony-best-practices/]Symfo
       ny best practices [2014]
     * [https://www.slideshare.net/javier.eguiluz/symfony-tips-and-tricks]
       Symfony tips and tricks [2014]
     * [https://emanueleminotto.github.io/blog/some-symfony-2-practices]So
       me Symfony 2 practices
     * [https://devel.cz/otazka/nette-vs-symfony#answer-17973]Výhody a
       nevýhody Symfony v bodech [2014] [cesky] - by
       [https://twitter.com/spicimedved]@spicimedved

Books

     * [https://leanpub.com/symfonyframeworkdeepdive-console]Symfony
       Framework Deepdive - Console [2015]
          + Detailed guide to Console Component by Joshua Thijssen
     * [https://leanpub.com/symfonyframeworkdeepdive-security]Symfony
       Framework Deepdive - Security [2015]
          + Detailed guide to Security Component by Joshua Thijssen
     * [https://leanpub.com/symfony-selfstudy]Symfony Certification -
       Unofficial self-study guide [2015]
          + Short Q-A based section about Symfony foundations
     * [https://leanpub.com/a-year-with-symfony]A Year with Symfony
       [updated 2014]
          + Great book for beginners to understand basic Symfony lifecycle
            and how to use it to your advantages.

